  "prompt": "Which is the best Android app locker?",
  "response": "The \"best\" Android app locker can vary depending on individual needs and preferences, but here are some of the most popular and highly-rated app lockers available on the Google Play Store:\n\n### 1. **Norton App Lock**\n   - **Features**: PIN, pattern, and fingerprint lock; stealth mode; break-in alerts.\n   - **Why It\u2019s Great**: Developed by Norton, a trusted name in security, it offers robust protection and additional features like stealth mode for added privacy.\n\n### 2. **AppLock by DoMobile Lab**\n   - **Features**: PIN, pattern, and fingerprint lock; fake cover; intruder selfie; break-in alerts.\n   - **Why It\u2019s Great**: One of the most popular app lockers, AppLock offers a wide range of features, including the ability to take a photo of someone who enters the wrong PIN.\n\n### 3. **Smart AppLock by Khalid Al-Kooheji**\n   - **Features**: PIN, pattern, and fingerprint lock; random keypad; stealth mode; break-in alerts.\n   - **Why It\u2019s Great**: Known for its simplicity and effectiveness, Smart AppLock provides reliable security with a clean interface.\n\n### 4. **CM Locker \u2013 Security Master, AppLock**\n   - **Features**: PIN, pattern, and fingerprint lock; intruder selfie; break-in alerts; secure browsing.\n   - **Why It\u2019s Great**: In addition to app locking, CM Locker offers a range of security features, including secure browsing and a cleaner.\n\n### 5. **MAX App Lock**\n   - **Features**: PIN, pattern, and fingerprint lock; fake cover; break-in alerts; hide app icon.\n   - **Why It\u2019s Great**: MAX App Lock is known for its user-friendly interface and additional features like a fake cover screen to confuse intruders.\n\n### 6. **Hi Locker**\n   - **Features**: Unlock with fingerprint, password, PIN, pattern, and draw.\n   - **Why It\u2019s Great**: Hi Locker not only locks apps but also provides a secondary interface for a secure space to store sensitive apps.\n\n### 7. **AppLock by SpSoft**\n   - **Features**: PIN, pattern, and fingerprint lock; intruder selfie; break-in alerts; hide app icon.\n   - **Why It\u2019s Great**: This app offers a simple yet effective way to lock apps and includes features like intruder selfie to enhance security.\n\n### Key Features to Consider When Choosing an App Locker:\n- **Security Options**: Multiple locking methods (PIN, pattern, fingerprint).\n- **Stealth Mode**: Ability to hide the app from the app drawer.\n- **Break-in Alerts**: Notifications or photos taken when someone tries to access locked apps.\n- **Fake Covers**: A fake crash screen or misleading message to confuse intruders.\n- **Additional Security Features**: Secure browsing, cleaner, or other tools.\n\n### Conclusion:\nFor most users, **Norton App Lock** and **AppLock by DoMobile Lab** are excellent choices due to their comprehensive features and reliability. However, the best app locker for you will depend on your specific needs and the additional features you prioritize. Always download app lockers from trusted sources and read reviews to ensure the app meets your security requirements.",
